CHANGES IN VERSION 0.1.*
------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o get_genome_files() to download FASTA and GTF files
    o add_seqs_to_gtf_and_fasta() to annotate user sequences to genome files
    o prime_fastq_files() prepare FASTQ sequences for alignment
    o retrieve_index() build and retrieve alignment index
    o perform_alignment() align FASTQ files to retrieved index
    o summarize_alignment() summarize alignment statistics
    o generate_count_matrix() quantify features from aligned files
